{"tid":1405822,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［唔好益狗鐵］每次遊行都要攞走賣票機嘅錢！","createTime":"2019-08-04T11:17:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T11:32:54.000Z","uid":44709,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"46f95666a630e899e5dab01549d11ec2105fb5c1","tid":1405822,"uid":44709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:17:35.000Z","msg":"眼見好多和理非嘅市民每次遊行/發夢完都會放一堆散紙散銀去賣票機 盡自己能力去幫手<br />\n雖然會攞嘅市民唔多<br />\n而且每次都淨番大量散紙喺機頂<br />\n但我都唔反對咁做 <br />\n因為真係好可能幫到有需要嘅人<br />\n<br />\n係依到我呼籲大家<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">每位發完夢/遊完行 搭尾班車走嘅市民，一定一定要攞走晒啲錢<br />\n攞番去捐比612或者其他有需要嘅機構</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望大家記得當日狗鐵喺元朗點對我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一千幾百都唔好益狗鐵！</span><br />\n<br />\n#我愛香港<br />\n#85一齊罷"},{"pid":"73bb1d60b703540ab9e71c9a4305907e5db11e29","tid":1405822,"uid":44709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:17:56.000Z","msg":"#85一齊罷"},{"pid":"b1528fcb902c4232ed2f0e780b1381d4ab343c9e","tid":1405822,"uid":44709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:18:46.000Z","msg":"#85一齊罷"},{"pid":"59a53eb817c8da258305c4caf3527abf83ad57ae","tid":1405822,"uid":44709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:19:02.000Z","msg":"#85一齊罷"},{"pid":"75f780ae83395113e69b2100009cd1a586160444","tid":1405822,"uid":44709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:19:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2defd949905f1b9ea46538656fde47dfacc87d47","tid":1405822,"uid":44709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:19:31.000Z","msg":"#85一齊罷"},{"pid":"92c5a0612d5ecb246ff228b658fe4e99e3ac9850","tid":1405822,"uid":44709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:19:42.000Z","msg":"#85一齊罷"},{"pid":"85994c84476bc2fe7a58fab6becdc49511452103","tid":1405822,"uid":44709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0